TITLE
    uSAC::Log - Wrapper for synch/ asynch logging

SYNOPSIS
      use uSAC::Log;

DESCRIPTION
    A shim pacakge to allow both synchrounus logging using Log::ger and
    asynchronous logging (when implemented ) in the upcoming uSAC
    distribution.

    If you don't know what any of those things are, do don't need this
    package !

    Primarily this would only be used if you intend to make a distri

